            <p>This Service does not explicitly use cookies. However, the app may utilize third-party code and libraries that use cookies to collect information and improve their services. You have the option to accept or refuse cookies and to know when a cookie is being sent to your device. Refusing cookies may limit your ability to use some portions of this Service.</p>
